{"word":"σήμερον","slug":"σήμερον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σήμερον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἡμέρα'><el>ἡμέρα</el></a> with <el>ς</el> prefixed\n<p/><i>to-day</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:—the common attic form was <el>τήμερον</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>εἰς τήμερον</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <el>ἡ τ. ἡμέρα</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}